1940;;New Moon;;American;;Jack Conway;;Jeanette MacDonald, Nelson Eddy;;musical drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Moon_(1940_film);;During the 18th century in New Orleans, Louisiana, a French nobleman in disguise as a bondsman, Charles (Nelson Eddy) leads his fellow bondsman in revolt against his ship's captain, commandeering the ship and heading out to sea.